"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d06954da6deeac25ff9f8344dab9c10fbacce83","tid":719203,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:03:22.000Z","msg":"幾時過西環唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91b61aed1e28b0072f474c4c91f5abd8aa5c151","tid":719203,"uid":20227,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:04:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e39cbbb35e84759dc35748f926ca0863851656cf","tid":719203,"uid":20227,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:06:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c12298c382c010d0dc01a7f547363633ccb1a23c","tid":719203,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:06:32.000Z","msg":"去d豪宅區啦"},{"pid":"46832edd5191755b83ee5b4663ce2f0dbf4f1a2b","tid":719203,"uid":15483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:13:53.000Z","msg":"遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff00dc1c9e217b4a891bf70aea9977de9d1cc64","tid":719203,"uid":187517,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be03cff888786acf3c71608aaba2185740cc594e","tid":719203,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2100000/2103222/20180627_laforet_01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2100000%2F2103222%2F20180627_laforet_01_1024.jpg&h=9a1ff1eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前旺角行人專用區「殺街」動議通過後，雖有人對此表示歡迎，可以為旺角帶來安寧，但同時有人擔心，這群經常高唱入雲的大媽會否轉到其他地方，繼續帶來聲音污染。事實總是 sad but ture 的，因為有網民貼圖提到「小喇叭大媽侵襲銅鑼灣東角道」，在 SOGO 東角道入口對面一帶，架好 iPad 歌譜，放置小喇叭高歌多首，讓途人盡享免費娛樂。<br />\n<br />\n最不期待的畫面出現了<br />\n<br />\n以上網民貼圖，意味大家最不期待的畫面，終於出現了，因此有網民直言：「預左啦，唔係銅鑼灣，就係天星碼頭」，更指這群大媽「到時可同法輪功，青關社 join 埋一齊表演」，「直頭恐怖份子」。甚至有網民表示：「等香港島嘅上等人受下」。<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣容得下小喇叭大媽？<br />\n<br />\n之不過，作為高尚地區的銅鑼灣，是否容得下小喇叭大媽呢？網友覺得：「銅鑼灣人不會像旺角咁低端接受大媽阻街」，以及「銅鑼灣係香港人神聖嘅地標！一定要趕佢哋走！因為班妖怪會影響市容！」希望這群小喇叭大媽的出現只是純屬偶然，如果他們真搬到銅鑼灣繼續帶來聲音污染的話，香港人假日又少了一個好去處了！<br />\n<br />\n網民有話兒：<br />\n<br />\n等香港島嘅上等人受下<br />\n唉，成條街殺咗，依家啲怪獸又揾其他地方寄居，好快連尖咀海傍到有大媽團<br />\n預左啦，唔係銅鑼灣，就係天星碼頭<br />\n到時可同法輪功，青關社 join 埋一齊表演<br />\n直頭恐怖份子<br />\n銅鑼灣係香港人神聖嘅地標！一定要趕佢哋走！因為班妖怪會影響市容！<br />\n唉，終於轉到銅鑼灣淪陷了<br />\n銅鑼灣人不會像旺角咁低端接受大媽阻街<br />\n禍港禍民&hellip;&hellip;大災難到&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n曱甴咁，唉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2100000/2103222/20180627_laforet_02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2100000%2F2103222%2F20180627_laforet_02_600.jpg&h=fb204e59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2100000/2103222/20180627_laforet_03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2100000%2F2103222%2F20180627_laforet_03_600.jpg&h=60850236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2100000/2103222/20180627_laforet_04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2100000%2F2103222%2F20180627_laforet_04_600.jpg&h=141debb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2103222/殺街後遺？小喇叭大媽入侵銅鑼灣東角道！網民：等港島嘅上等人受下\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2103222%2F%E6%AE%BA%E8%A1%97%E5%BE%8C%E9%81%BA%EF%BC%9F%E5%B0%8F%E5%96%87%E5%8F%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E5%85%A5%E4%BE%B5%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%